datasetVersion.versionNote: PDF packs for each state contain maps of Reserve Component service members deployed to OIF/OEF since 9/11/2001 and their dependents, a table of totals by county, spatial analysis of driving distances from service members by zip code to nearest VA facility, and a deployment chart.
